PrecisAcceptance of an AMENDMENT OF SURRENDER duly assented to by the MOWACHAHT/ MUCHALAHT BAND whereby the use of Ahaminaquus Indian Reserve No. 12 in British Columbia, which the Band surrendered in 1963 for leasing purposes, will be restricted to industrial and commercial uses and the duration of the designation will be restricted to seventy (70) years.
